# 🐞 bug report
After upgrading to 8.0.1, Service Worker doesn't seem to register any longer. If I register it manually it works. Please note I'm NOT using IVY.

```
In Main Module
# This does NOT work any longer (used to, haven't changed anything)
ServiceWorkerModule.register('/ngsw-worker.js', { enabled: true })

```

But if I register manually during app bootstrap it works:

```
platformBrowserDynamic().bootstrapModule(AppModule).then(() => {
  if ('serviceWorker' in navigator && environment.production) {
    navigator.serviceWorker.register('/ngsw-worker.js');
  }
}).catch(err => console.log(err));

```






